oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Proceedings of the Twenty-Seventh Annual Conference (1994). 18th World Buiatrics Congress
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The 18th World Buiatrics Congress was held in conjunction with the 26th Italian Buiatrics Congress on August 29 - September 2, 1994 in Bologna, Italy. 1050 delegates and 130 accompanying persons from 42 countries participated in the scientific and social programs. Many topics related to cattle diseases were presented in 168 oral and 171 poster communications. There were also 4 Satellite Symposia.
